				<h1 class="headline" style="text-align:center;">Obama's Secret Iran Strategy</h1>
				<div class="excerpt"><p class="p1">The president has long been criticized for his lack of strategic vision. But what if a strategy, centered on Iran, has been in place from the start and consistently followed to this day?</p>
</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	
