		<div class="post_separator post_separator_response"></div>
	</div>	<div class="item_container item_container_response item_container_5167" id="item_container_5167">
		<div class="essay_container">
			<div class="essay_title_container">
				<h1 class="headline" style="text-align:center;">The Obama Doctrine</h1>
				<div class="excerpt"><p>An ideological aversion to American power is at the core of the president&#8217;s foreign policy.</p>
</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	
		<div class="essay_container" id="essay_container_5167" data-permalink="http://mosaicmagazine.com/response/2015/02/the-obama-doctrine-constraining-american-power/">
			<img class="main_image" src="//mosaicmagazine.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/Edelman-Main.jpg?5f1008" width="830" alt="The Obama Doctrine" /><br />
			<span class="image_caption">Official White House photo, Pete Souza.</span>

			<div>
				<!-- COL ONE -->
				<div class="column one alpha">&nbsp;<!-- Blank... --></div>

				<!-- DEFINE this area so that LH sidebar has a boundary -->
				<div class="column four omega" id="post_body_5167">
					<!-- COL TWO -->
					<div class="column one essay_sidebar">
						<div class="fp_subitem_title fp_type_response">Response</div><div class="fp_subitem_subtitle"><a class="author_href" href="http://mosaicmagazine.com/author/eric-edelman/">Eric Edelman</a></div><div class="fp_subitem_date">Feb. 16 2015</div><div class="author_bio"><strong>About the author</strong><br /><p><span style="color: #000000;">Eric Edelman, a f</span><span style="color: #000000;">ormer Under Secretary of Defense for Policy and former U.S. ambassador to Turkey, is Hertog distinguished practitioner in residence at the Johns Hopkins School of Advanced International Studies.</span></p>
</div>			
						<hr />
					
						<div class="essay_control_links" id="essay_control_links_5167">
