			<div class="essay_title_container">
				<h1 class="headline" style="text-align:center;">What They're Saying about "Obama's Secret Iran Strategy"</h1>
				<div class="excerpt"><p>Michael Doran&#8217;s essay provoked a &#8220;firestorm in the policy world.&#8221; Here&#8217;s a roundup of arguments for and against his thesis.</p>
</div>
