		<div class="essay_container" id="essay_container_5234" data-permalink="http://mosaicmagazine.com/response/2015/02/what-theyre-saying-about-obamas-secret-iran-strategy/">
			<img class="main_image" src="//mosaicmagazine.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/Outside-Home-Main.jpg?5f1008" width="830" alt="What They&#039;re Saying about &quot;Obama&#039;s Secret Iran Strategy&quot;" /><br />
