						<div class="fp_subitem_title fp_type_response">Response</div><div class="fp_subitem_subtitle"><a class="author_href" href="http://mosaicmagazine.com/author/the-editors/">The Editors</a></div><div class="fp_subitem_date">Feb. 19 2015</div><div class="author_bio"></div>			
