		<div class="essay_container">
			<div class="essay_title_container">
				<h1 class="headline" style="text-align:center;">The Reform Delusion</h1>
				<div class="excerpt"><p>Bright people in Washington have long dreamed about the possibility of a reformed Iran. Barack Obama is just the latest.</p>
</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	
		<div class="essay_container" id="essay_container_5319" data-permalink="http://mosaicmagazine.com/response/2015/02/the-reform-delusion/">
			<img class="main_image" src="//mosaicmagazine.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/Gerecht-Home-Main.jpg?5f1008" width="830" alt="The Reform Delusion" /><br />
			<span class="image_caption">Official White House photo, Pete Souza.</span>

			<div>
				<!-- COL ONE -->
				<div class="column one alpha">&nbsp;<!-- Blank... --></div>

